        "heading_gN6jAB": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What’s new in Mission Rewards",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_hiMjBf": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>We’ve made some exciting changes to Mission Rewards – all designed to make your experience simpler, clearer, and more rewarding from the start.</p><p>Here’s what’s new:</p><ul><li><strong>Free shipping on case buys</strong> – Buy a 6-pack or more of wine and receive free shipping!</li><li><strong>No more tiers</strong> – We’ve removed the tier system based on your feedback. Now, everyone earns points and enjoys perks without needing to level up.</li><li><strong>Simplified points and redemptions</strong> – Earn 1 point for every $1 you spend, and redeem 400 points for a $50 voucher.</li><li><strong>Social sharing & referrals</strong> – Earn points when you follow or share Mission Estate on Instagram or Facebook, or refer a friend.</li><li><strong>Wallet balances still valid</strong> – If you had credits in your old Mission Rewards wallet, you will have received an online code for their value; just make sure to redeem them within three years of the upgrade.</li></ul><p>This new programme is fully integrated with our online store – making it easier than ever to earn points and access perks.</p>",
            "font_desk": 18,
            "font_mob": 14
          }
        },
        "button_6qdEVT": {
          "type": "button",
          "settings": {
            "button_label": "Read the full FAQ here",
