        "text_aktyh7": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Disclosure and Terms:</strong> <br/><em>Mission Rewards is intended to thank customers for their loyalty. Rewards are not transferable, have no cash value, and are subject to change or expiry. Discounts and point offers exclude alcohol purchases where prohibited by law. We encourage the responsible enjoyment of wine at all times.</em></p><p><strong>NB. Mission Rewards cannot be accrued, earned or redeemed in the Mission Estate Restaurant or Concert.</strong></p><p><em>Have more questions? Visit our full </em><a href=\"https://1yyktp-yk.myshopify.com/pages/mission-rewards-faq\" title=\"https://1yyktp-yk.myshopify.com/pages/mission-rewards-faq\"><em>Mission Rewards FAQ </em></a><em>to learn more about earning points, redeeming rewards, and what’s changed. </em></p><p><a href=\"/pages/mission-rewards-terms-conditions\" title=\"Mission Rewards Terms & Conditions\"><em>Read the Mission Rewards Term & Conditions</em></a></p>",
